  "texts": [
    "A systemized multi-season database of BSF production and processing from a pilot facility producing above average volumes is used to conduct an LCA for BSFL products.",
    "In order to define more sustainable solutions, these data are then analysed using attributional (definition of the best production and allocation amongst products) and consequential life cycle assessment methodologies (Smetana et al., 2019).",
    "Life cycle assessment containing the steps as Gaol and scope, Life cycle inventory.",
    "Life cycle impact assessment and Interpretation of black soldier fly farming for animal feed and fertilizer is depicted in Fig. 3.",
    "The production of insects is about to go from a pilot scale to an industrial scale."
  ]
